<div class="cards">
	<div class="form-block">

	<h4>还没有激活您的会员卡，请按以下提示操作，激活您的VIP卡 </h4>
	<%link_to '暂不激活', root_path, class:'button hollow alert'%>
	<%link_to '去激活会员卡' '#', class:'button alert'%>




		<h4>您还没有激活您的会员卡，请按以下提示操作，激活您的VIP卡 </h4>

		<p>请填写您的VIP卡号或手机号码 : </p>

		<div class="field">
			<%=radio_button_tag :activate_type,'card_no',:checked=>true%>
			<label for="activate_type_card_no" class="radio-label">VIP卡号</label>

			<%=radio_button_tag :activate_type,'user_tel'%>
			<label for="activate_type_user_tel" class="radio-label">手机号码</label>
		</div>

		<%=form_for :search, :url=>search_card_path,:method=>:get,:html=>{:class=>"card_no"} do |f|%>
			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label">VIP卡号 : </label>
				<%=f.text_field :no,:value=>params[:search]&&params[:search][:no],:class=>"field-input"%>
				<span class="error"><%=flash[:error]%></span>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<%=f.submit "确认卡号",:class=>"btn submit"%>
			</div>
		<%end%>

		<%=form_for :search, :url=>search_card_path,:method=>:get,:html=>{:class=>"user_tel"} do |f|%>
			
			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label">手机号码 : </label>
				<%=f.text_field :user_tel,:class=>"field-input"%>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<%=f.submit "查询卡号",:class=>"btn submit"%>
			</div>
		<%end%>

	</div>
	<div class="tips-block">
		<p>小贴士</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>如何激活我的VIP卡?</strong>
				<div>答：请按左侧提示，完成操作即可激活您的VIP卡。</div>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>怎么用VIP卡里的余额付款？</strong>
				<div>答：在您完成VIP卡激活后，您的VIP卡余额将会存入你当前登录用户名的预存款账户中，您只需要在购物时选择“预存款支付”方式支付即可。</div>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
	<div class="other-tip "> <span class="required">*</span> 小贴士 :  如果在激活过程中有什么疑问，请致电寻求帮助。客服电话：021 - 22306630。</div>
	
</div>

            <div class="row">                    
                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                    <h1>会员卡激活</h1>
                    <p> </p>    
                    <p>
                    <% if @user.errors.any? %> 
                    <div id="error_explanation" style="color:red">
                        <ul> 
                        <% @user.errors.full_messages.each do |msg| %> 
                            <li><%= msg %></li> 
                        <% end %> 
                        </ul> 
                    </div> 
                    <% end %>

                    </p>                    
